Welcome to Our Story
Welcome to Bearded Brothers Taphouse & Eatery, where Italian heritage meets the love for craft brews and delicious food. Founded by brothers Gaetano and Liborio Traina, our establishment is a culmination of their upbringing in the restaurant industry under the guidance of their father, Francesco Traina, who owned pizzerias across the Palm Bay area.
Inspired by their family's culinary legacy and fueled by their passion for flavorful brews, Gaetano and Liborio decided to venture beyond the realm of pizza and dive into the world of hops. Bearded Brothers Taphouse & Eatery is a testament to their dedication to providing patrons with an unforgettable dining experience, blending flavorful craft food with an extensive selection of craft beers and wine.
Whether you're seeking a hearty meal paired with a refreshing brew or simply looking to un-wine in a welcoming atmosphere, Bearded Brothers Taphouse & Eatery invites you to indulge in the fusion of tradition and innovation, where every bite and sip tells a story of passion and quality.
